ayer forges can contain soldiers for defense like villages towers but like towers do not produce additional soldiers for player support them forges increase attack ability defense ability all soldiers player who controls them gameplay divided into three categories campaign skirmish local multiplayer three difficulty levels exist allowing player increase challenge after getting hang game campaign mode there are various mission scenarios where player can play against up three computer-controlled opponents campaign battles often have goals such capturing all enemy points before time expires capturing key villages simply capturing all enemy villages with no time restrictions skirmish mode provides wide variety maps for single player action against up three computer-controlled opponents local multiplayer mode allows up four players play against each other users may also unlock online multiplayer via psn add-on purchase game has inviting light-hearted tone controls are relatively simple compared other rts games artwork bright cartoon like colorful references mushroom wars for ipad on itunes app store itunesapplecom retrieved new releases war tanks mushroom wars creative-mobilecom/ retrieved catogoryxbox one xbox retrieved from https//enwikipediaorg/w/indexphptitle=mushroomwars&oldid=739601323 categories video games android operating system games ios games real-time strategy video games playstation network games playstation games windows games hidden categories articles needing additional references from march all articles needing additional references navigation menu personal tools not logged talk contributions create account log namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main page contents featured content current events random article donate wikipedia wikipedia store interaction help about wikipedia community portal recent changes contact page tools what links here related changes upload file special pages permanent link page in